Information About Cohorts from TCGA Project

Function restores codes and counts for each cohort from TCGA project.

infoTCGA()

Value

A list with a tabular information from http://gdac.broadinstitute.org/.

Issues

If you have any problems, issues or think that something is missing or is not clear please post an issue on https://github.com/RTCGA/RTCGA/issues.

See also

RTCGA website http://rtcga.github.io/RTCGA/Download.html.

Other RTCGA: RTCGA-package, boxplotTCGA, checkTCGA, convertTCGA, createTCGA, datasetsTCGA, downloadTCGA, expressionsTCGA, heatmapTCGA, installTCGA, kmTCGA, mutationsTCGA, pcaTCGA, readTCGA, survivalTCGA, theme_RTCGA

library(magrittr)
(cohorts <- infoTCGA() %>%
rownames() %>%
   sub('-counts', '', x=.))
